nodes.text: TIE Fighter 3 is the third issue of the canon comic book miniseries Star Wars: TIE Fighter. It was written by Jody Houser, illustrated by Rogê Antônio and Geraldo Borges, and published on June 19, 2019 by Marvel Comics.
THE NET CLOSES! The traitors of the REBEL ALLIANCE have made their presence known! Will the heroes of the EMPIRE be able to salvage the mission and save the day? And at what cost?
